DIA_OPEN.text: Hey there  I m Professor Fennel, AsŇyou can see  I m a scientist, InŇfact  the subject I m researching isŇTrainers ȼMy dream is to collect save files ofŇvarious trainers  but I haven t hadŇany breakthroughs yet,,,ȼSo in the meantime  I ve been workingŇon a different project with one of myŇold friends ȼIn my home region  there s a locationŇthat can make a Pok mon s dreams intoŇreality,ȼThis means that any other Pok monŇthey meet in their dreams becomeŇreal ȼThat s fantastic  but my goal is toŇdo the same  just with a trainer sŇdream instead  That s why I need yourŇhelp ȼI want to bring as many Pok mon outŇof your dreams as possible ȼThere s just over 250 Pok mon I wantŇto catalogue in my Dream Pok Dex  orŇDream Dex for short,ȼBut I ll let you keep any Pok mon Ňthey re from your dreams after all ȼOne last note  save data backups areŇrecommended  just on the off chanceŇthat something goes wrong ŇI think that s everything,,,ȼwhenever you re ready to start  justŇlet me know ƞ

DIA_E4.text: Hi trainer  I m thrilled you veŇdecided to help with our research Ňbut we need the best of the best ȼCome back after you ve beaten theŇElite Four and become the Champion ƞ

DIA_MG_FRLGE.text: Sorry trainer  one more thing to takeŇcare of before we can begin  you needŇto enable MYSTERY GIFT ȼHead to the nearest Pok  Mart andŇfill out the questionnaire asŇfollows: LINK TOGETHER WITH ALL,ȼAfter that  you should be all set toŇgo  See you soon ƞ

DIA_MG_RS.text: Sorry trainer  one more thing to takeŇcare of before we can begin  you needŇto enable MYSTERY EVENT ȼHead to the PETALBURG Pok mon CenterŇand tell the man next to the PC:ŇMYSTERY EVENT IS EXCITING, AfterŇthat  you should be all set to go ȼSee you soon ƞ

DIA_LETS_START.text: Perfect  that s all the information IŇneed  Let s get started ƞ

DIA_START.text: On a second Game Boy family system Ňplease load the Game Boy Pok mon gameŇyou wish to transfer from,ȼIn your Game Boy Pok mon game  makeŇyour current box the one you want toŇtransfer from,ȼThen connect this Game Boy Advance toŇthe other Game Boy family systemŇusing a Game Boy Color link cable,ȼOnce you re ready  press A on thisŇdevice  talk to the Cable ClubŇattendant  and then initiate a trade,ƞ

DIA_NEW_DEX.text: It looks like there s at least oneŇnew Pok mon here that isn t in theŇDream Dex  I ll give them somethingŇextra sweet as a reward for you both,ƞ

DIA_NO_NEW_DEX.text: It doesn t look like there s anythingŇnew for your Dream Dex  but that sŇokay  It s important to confirmŇresearch results with multiple tests ƞ

DIA_SEND_FRIEND_KANTO.text: I m going to send these Pok mon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up  They live just south ofŇthe Pok mon center on Seven Island ƞ

DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_RS.text: I m going to send these Pok mon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up ȼThey live just southeast of theŇPok mon center in Mossdeep City ƞ

DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_E.text: I m going to send these Pok mon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up ȼThey live just southeast of theŇPok mon center in Sootopolis City ƞ

DIA_THANK.text: Thank you so much for your help ŇWhenever you want to transfer moreŇPok mon  just let me know  See youŇaround ƞ

DIA_MG_OTHER_EVENT.text: Hi Trainer  It looks like you have aŇdifferent event currently loaded,ŇThat s no problem  but it will beŇoverwritten if you continue,ȼTurn off the system now if you wantŇto experience your current event  butŇotherwise ƞ

DIA_PKMN_TO_COLLECT.text: Hi Trainer  It looks like you stillŇhave Pok mon to pick up,,, I can tŇsend over new Pok mon until you pickŇthose up,ȼCome back after you ve received them ƞ

DIA_NO_VALID_PKMN.text: Sorry Trainer  it doesn t look likeŇyou have any valid Pok mon in yourŇcurrent box right now,ȼGo double check your current box andŇwe can give it another shot ƞ

DIA_ASK_QUEST.text: Hi trainer  Before we begin  I needŇto ask you a few questions,ƞ

DIA_WHAT_GAME_TRANS.text: And which Game Boy Pok mon game areŇyou transferring from ƞ

DIA_WHAT_LANG_TRANS.text: What language is the Game Boy Pok monŇgame that you re transferring from ƞ

DIA_NO_GB_ROM.text: I m sorry  but that version in thatŇlanguage is not currently supported,ƞ

DIA_IN_BOX.text: Alright  Let s take a look at theŇPok mon that will be transfered,ȼPlease remember  once a Pok mon isŇtransfered  it CANNOT be returned toŇthe Game Boy Game Pak,ȼSelect confirm once you re ready  orŇselect cancel if you want to keep theŇPok mon on your Game Boy Game Pak,ƞ

DIA_MYTHIC_CONVERT.text: It looks like you have a rareŇMythical Pok mon  Due to theirŇrarity  it seems they ve overloadedŇthe machine,ȼI can stablize them if you d like Ňbut it ll change some things like metŇlocation  OT  TID  and Shininess,ȼOtherwise I can leave them as is  butŇthere s no guarentee that they ll beŇtransferrable in the future, Do youŇwant me to stablize them ȼThis will apply to all of theŇMythical Pok mon currently in yourŇbox,ƞ

DIA_CANCEL.text: No worries  Feel free to come back ifŇyou change your mind  See you around ƞ

DIA_SOME_INVALID_PKMN.text: I see there is at least one Pok monŇthat cannot be transferred from yourŇcurrent box,ȼPok mon holding items or modifiedŇincorrectly through unintended meansŇcannot be transferred,ȼThe other Pok mon will transfer justŇfine though ƞ

DIA_MENU_BACK.text: No worries  Feel free to come backŇany time ƞ

DIA_OPEN.text: Hey there! I’m Professor Fennel. AsŇyou can see, I’m a scientist. InŇfact, the subject I’m researching isŇTrainers!ȼMy dream is to collect save files ofŇvarious trainers, but I haven’t hadŇany breakthroughs yet...ȼSo in the meantime, I’ve been workingŇon a different project with one of myŇold friends!ȼIn my home region, there’s a locationŇthat can make a Pokémon’s dreams intoŇreality.ȼThis means that any other PokémonŇthey meet in their dreams becomeŇreal!ȼThat’s fantastic, but my goal is toŇdo the same- just with a trainer’sŇdream instead! That’s why I need yourŇhelp!ȼI want to bring as many Pokémon outŇof your dreams as possible!ȼThere’s just over 250 Pokémon I wantŇto catalogue in my Dream PokéDex- orŇDream Dex for short.ȼBut I’ll let you keep any Pokémon-Ňthey’re from your dreams after all!ȼOne last note, save data backups areŇrecommended- just on the off chanceŇthat something goes wrong!ŇI think that’s everything...ȼwhenever you’re ready to start, justŇlet me know!ƞ

DIA_E4.text: Hi trainer! I’m thrilled you’veŇdecided to help with our research,Ňbut we need the best of the best!ȼCome back after you’ve beaten theŇElite Four and become the Champion!ƞ

DIA_MG_FRLGE.text: Sorry trainer, one more thing to takeŇcare of before we can begin- you needŇto enable MYSTERY GIFT!ȼHead to the nearest Poké Mart andŇfill out the questionnaire asŇfollows: LINK TOGETHER WITH ALL.ȼAfter that, you should be all set toŇgo! See you soon!ƞ

DIA_MG_RS.text: Sorry trainer, one more thing to takeŇcare of before we can begin- you needŇto enable MYSTERY EVENT!ȼHead to the PETALBURG Pokémon CenterŇand tell the man next to the PC:ŇMYSTERY EVENT IS EXCITING. AfterŇthat, you should be all set to go!ȼSee you soon!ƞ

DIA_LETS_START.text: Perfect, that’s all the information IŇneed! Let’s get started!ƞ

DIA_START.text: On a second Game Boy family system,Ňplease load the Game Boy Pokémon gameŇyou wish to transfer from.ȼIn your Game Boy Pokémon game, makeŇyour current box the one you want toŇtransfer from.ȼThen connect this Game Boy Advance toŇthe other Game Boy family systemŇusing a Game Boy Color link cable.ȼOnce you’re ready, press A on thisŇdevice, talk to the Cable ClubŇattendant, and then initiate a trade.ƞ

DIA_NEW_DEX.text: It looks like there’s at least oneŇnew Pokémon here that isn’t in theŇDream Dex! I’ll give them somethingŇextra sweet as a reward for you both.ƞ

DIA_NO_NEW_DEX.text: It doesn’t look like there’s anythingŇnew for your Dream Dex, but that’sŇokay! It’s important to confirmŇresearch results with multiple tests!ƞ

DIA_SEND_FRIEND_KANTO.text: I’m going to send these Pokémon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up! They live just south ofŇthe Pokémon center on Seven Island!ƞ

DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_RS.text: I’m going to send these Pokémon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up!ȼThey live just southeast of theŇPokémon center in Mossdeep City!ƞ

DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_E.text: I’m going to send these Pokémon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up!ȼThey live just southeast of theŇPokémon center in Sootopolis City!ƞ

DIA_THANK.text: Thank you so much for your help!ŇWhenever you want to transfer moreŇPokémon, just let me know! See youŇaround!ƞ

DIA_MG_OTHER_EVENT.text: Hi Trainer! It looks like you have aŇdifferent event currently loaded.ŇThat’s no problem, but it will beŇoverwritten if you continue.ȼTurn off the system now if you wantŇto experience your current event, butŇotherwise-ƞ

DIA_PKMN_TO_COLLECT.text: Hi Trainer! It looks like you stillŇhave Pokémon to pick up... I can’tŇsend over new Pokémon until you pickŇthose up.ȼCome back after you’ve received them!ƞ

DIA_NO_VALID_PKMN.text: Sorry Trainer, it doesn’t look likeŇyou have any valid Pokémon in yourŇcurrent box right now.ȼGo double check your current box andŇwe can give it another shot!ƞ

DIA_ASK_QUEST.text: Hi trainer! Before we begin, I needŇto ask you a few questions.ƞ

DIA_WHAT_GAME_TRANS.text: And which Game Boy Pokémon game areŇyou transferring from?ƞ

DIA_WHAT_LANG_TRANS.text: What language is the Game Boy PokémonŇgame that you’re transferring from?ƞ

DIA_NO_GB_ROM.text: I’m sorry, but that version in thatŇlanguage is not currently supported.ƞ

DIA_IN_BOX.text: Alright! Let’s take a look at theŇPokémon that will be transfered.ȼPlease remember, once a Pokémon isŇtransfered, it CANNOT be returned toŇthe Game Boy Game Pak.ȼSelect confirm once you’re ready, orŇselect cancel if you want to keep theŇPokémon on your Game Boy Game Pak.ƞ

DIA_MYTHIC_CONVERT.text: It looks like you have a rareŇMythical Pokémon! Due to theirŇrarity, it seems they’ve overloadedŇthe machine.ȼI can stablize them if you’d like,Ňbut it’ll change some things like metŇlocation, OT, TID, and Shininess.ȼOtherwise I can leave them as is, butŇthere’s no guarentee that they’ll beŇtransferrable in the future. Do youŇwant me to stablize them?ȼThis will apply to all of theŇMythical Pokémon currently in yourŇbox.ƞ

DIA_CANCEL.text: No worries! Feel free to come back ifŇyou change your mind! See you around!ƞ

DIA_SOME_INVALID_PKMN.text: I see there is at least one PokémonŇthat cannot be transferred from yourŇcurrent box.ȼPokémon holding items or modifiedŇincorrectly through unintended meansŇcannot be transferred.ȼThe other Pokémon will transfer justŇfine though!ƞ

DIA_MENU_BACK.text: No worries! Feel free to come backŇany time!ƞ

DIA_IS_MISSINGNO.text: ... It seems like one of your PokémonŇis messing with the machine... ItŇlooks to only be graphical though, soŇwe can continue!ƞ

DIA_ERROR_COLOSSEUM.text: It looks like you went to theŇcolosseum instead of the tradingŇroom! Let’s try that again!ƞ

DIA_ERROR_COM_ENDED.text: Communication with the other deviceŇwas terminated. Let’s try that again!ƞ

DIA_ERROR_DISCONNECT.text: It looks like the Game Boy Color linkŇcable was disconnected... Let’s tryŇthat again!ƞ

DIA_ERROR_TIME_ONE.text: It looks like the connection timedŇout... Let’s try that again!ƞ

DIA_ERROR_TIME_TWO.text: It seems like the connection timedŇout... Let’s try that again!ƞ

DIA_WHAT_GAME_EVENT.text: And which Game Boy Pokémon game doŇyou want to send an event to?ƞ

DIA_J_DEX_NOT_FULL.text: Sorry trainer, it looks like youŇhaven’t caught all 99 new PokémonŇfrom the Johto region yet.ȼGo out and catch them all and thenŇwe’ll be able to send over the event!ƞ
